    <item>
      <title>“咆哮的小猫”和会议故障让 GameStop 踏上疯狂之旅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/-roaring-kitty-meeting-snafu-send-gamestop-on-wild-round-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于 GameStop Corp. 的投资者来说，过去的两周非常忙碌 — — 包括一次因技术故障而被迫中止的年度股东大会以及该公司最引人注目的股东调整其投资组合 — — 导致股价基本回到了最初的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/-roaring-kitty-meeting-snafu-send-gamestop-on-wild-round-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
